{"tid":311820,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[router撚][JJ插地核求救]想問吓點樣駁兩個router","createTime":"2017-07-07T02:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T06:46:55.000Z","uid":88344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6269a70f00cb0e46d6becabec13c14ab94097b87","tid":311820,"uid":88344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:46:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟就想駁多個router，方便打機可以更新得快啲，咁啱打機嗰個位就係死位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />收唔到wifi乜滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早兩日喺屋企搵到個舊嘅router，但都仲用到的，所以就想駁吓，點知去到set up嗰陣就出咗啲問題，話我個wan唔啱類型，過唔到驗證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家嘅情況就係本身有一個router，牌子係asus (rt-n56u)，呢個駁咗喺房到，連住房入面嘅電腦。<br />\n<br />\n另一個係tp-link (TL-wr740n)，諗住駁喺廳，點知set up唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身喺房入面有一個電源分插(一對對嗰啲插蘇)，將條lan線就分出廳俾廳部電腦，諗住用分出黎嗰條lan線駁，唔知係咪咁樣jam咗個ip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以setup唔到。<br />\n<br />\n唔該各路英雄請教吓小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果成功打到機，小弟真係會無限感激你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n如果我嘅配置係駁唔到2個router，請問我應該點樣做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374e56fadaf816ded03ae8f89444b9f152feb067","tid":311820,"uid":88344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:34:39.000Z","msg":"毒撚開post 冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9cae370853d0a442d53eb035ab3763d06b7f05","tid":311820,"uid":34955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:57:42.000Z","msg":"1. 熄舊果部嘅DHCP Server功能<br />\n2. rt-n56u拉一條線出黎插舊router lan1"},{"pid":"343bb43cbb4b8d0ca0e6aa0d962b4f107d43ee4f","tid":311820,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:59:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 熄舊果部嘅DHCP Server功能<br />\n2. rt-n56u拉一條線出黎插舊router lan1</blockquote><br />\n意思即係用n56u做主router，TPlink做AP剩係負責放wifi同lan頭"},{"pid":"8e29c515f1fe831a62a8f187af5987d4f71cc42c","tid":311820,"uid":88344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T05:21:39.000Z","msg":"我想問吓 咁asus嗰個router 熄咗dchp之後<br />\n會唔會用唔到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07db3ac696094b634c79e4f6a94568824590e023","tid":311820,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問吓 咁asus嗰個router 熄咗dchp之後<br />\n會唔會用唔到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主router唔好熄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1482fd97a881a79d5dac092a6d20812a1154021d","tid":311820,"uid":88344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:07:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想問吓 咁asus嗰個router 熄咗dchp之後<br />\n會唔會用唔到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主router唔好熄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好意思 咩都唔識<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6ed2dc4f751a486ae22508599ba1cf25a519af","tid":311820,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想問吓 咁asus嗰個router 熄咗dchp之後<br />\n會唔會用唔到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主router唔好熄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家先睇到，原來56u先係舊router<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之勁果隻(56U)駁出街+用default setting<br />\n廢果部熄DHCP<br />\n由勁果部拉條LAN線插廢果部嘅時候唔好插落WAN頭，插LAN1"},{"pid":"53acdc56f34d76a30ccc6f2909f5d5a0d44535fe","tid":311820,"uid":88344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想問吓 咁asus嗰個router 熄咗dchp之後<br />\n會唔會用唔到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主router唔好熄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家先睇到，原來56u先係舊router<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之勁果隻(56U)駁出街+用default setting<br />\n廢果部熄DHCP<br />\n由勁果部拉條LAN線插廢果部嘅時候唔好插落WAN頭，插LAN1</blockquote><br />\n番去即刻攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先行謝過ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}